

	Need simple idea which cannot be divided further

	build by using the simple idea as base to build complex ideas

	get into flow state in constructing

	recalling the construction process reinforces the idea's memory

	Every thing will be build on this simple idea only always start construction complex idea from this simple idea

	Adding experiences enhances the reenforce process more strong

	Start from what you know and build to the concept

	By connecting the ideas which you know to ideas which you are not familiar with

	Bringin the life to the words is the main process in extracting knowledge from words (not understanding)

	we can only manipulate an idea if we are familiar with the basic blocks (mastering)

	
